{"tid":644613,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[再戰奶茶] 捷榮下周一招股","createTime":"2018-04-27T10:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T15:31:05.000Z","uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"727d5c08c5e708455b04fbc47e4d617c2d83c6ae","tid":644613,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"【奶茶新股】捷榮下周一招股 主席黃達堂賣55%舊股<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180427/large/1524823112_8b68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180427%2Flarge%2F1524823112_8b68.jpg&h=97230c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捷榮（2119）下周一開招，全球發行2.392億股，但其中55%為舊股。售股股東、捷榮主席黃達堂表示，上市的首要目的是為了引入基礎投資者，集資非重點，「如果我自己走咗去，佢哋都唔肯過我。」黃達堂上市後持有捷榮約66%股權。<br />\n<br />\n捷榮的最大客戶麥當勞，去年被中信股份（267）收購。捷榮營運總監鄔表示，與麥當勞新管理層有緊密聯繫，作定期溝通。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今次冇得輸</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54eeb2c21ad61a059ae53a125accde2ce8574764","tid":644613,"uid":3122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"星如係度做乜"},{"pid":"47dc8dbd5bcb1f49a2c43d0f45eec40c2e207dcb","tid":644613,"uid":73647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"一定又超認購率"},{"pid":"674ef53d47a69617939f2b644af3f8edfc8d46e1","tid":644613,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"平安d錢應該回得切"},{"pid":"9ad4dc189decf68fb87b537926b7da3b26a169ef","tid":644613,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54eeb2c21ad61a059ae53a125accde2ce8574764","tid":644613,"uid":3122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"星如係度做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyT